goals__remit: The Royal Dutch Grain and Feed Trade Association (‘Het Comité’) is a trade organisation representing the interests of its approximately 120 members in the agri-business. Its activities also include compiling and managing standard national and international trade contracts, operating an arbitration institute, organising an annual course in grain trading and setting day values.
